{"tid":1008110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 逛花市遇長者問為何沒獲發4千元　特首笑說研究下","createTime":"2019-02-04T08:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T04:38:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"19ed7bba96fb9fd90d9e0395e1f8481e43b87adb","tid":1008110,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:59:14.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥先到一個攤檔用68元購買花盆裝飾，再到另一檔用152元購買兩罐蛋卷，並與檔主交談，期間與在場市民及小孩拍照留念及傾談，又與市民互祝新年快樂、身體健康等。她與區議員手持揮春合照，說大家同心，香港一定會更好。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又與一名坐輪椅的長者聊天，長者問她為何沒有獲派4000元派，她笑說要研究下。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥逗留約半小時後離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441480-20190204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441480-20190204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=d2bdbcfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441480-20190204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dac40afd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441480-20190204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3e4ae371ccda71b4a475f3cea96621b512e0ee77","tid":1008110,"uid":19552,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母幾個月前派左比佢地先"},{"pid":"1fdf96a66d252a15191f34ea6374d1b8717d85e2","tid":1008110,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"why 硏究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想取消？"},{"pid":"bff83291d8e68075dc67bb1d81458b140694e975","tid":1008110,"uid":37733,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3e4ae371ccda71b4a475f3cea96621b512e0ee77","tid":1008110,"uid":19552,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母幾個月前派左比佢地先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"綜援三糧還綜援三糧<br />\n我要埋額外4000蚊<im